OPAL v3 provides interfaces to access the chips XSCOM, expose
this via the existing scom infrastructure.

Signed-off-by: Benjamin Herrenschmidt <benh@kernel.crashing.org>
Acked-by: Torsten Duwe <duwe@suse.de>

